dc_title_s: Map of the Lower Cuyahoga River Basin and adjacent Lake Erie tributaries showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|Scale bar lower left corner of map.|"Prepared by ALFRED C.
